 abnormal event between 2025-06-09T00:10:25Z and 2025-06-09T00:34:25Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-09 00:10:25+00:00 to 2025-06-09 00:34:25+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "基于日志分析结果，我现在处于初始扫描阶段。让我分析这些日志数据并提取关键信息。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"DeadlineExceeded\",\n    \"context deadline exceeded\",\n    \"adservice--gc\",\n    \"GCHelper\",\n    \"InvocationTargetException\",\n    \"Byteman agent\",\n    \"Agent failed to start\",\n    \"Rule.execute\",\n    \"gc helper trigger gc\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice 存在 GC (垃圾回收) 异常，Byteman agent 多次加载失败导致服务不可用\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Rule.execute called for AdService--gc-1749427826_16:0, Agent failed to start!, Exception in thread \\\"Attach Listener\\\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend 调用 adservice 时出现 DeadlineExceeded 超时错误，表明 adservice 响应异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n在异常时间段 2025-06-09T00:10:25Z 至 2025-06-09T00:34:25Z 内，发现了以下关键问题：\n\n### 主要异常模式：\n1. **adservice 的 GC 异常**：检测到 `adservice--gc` 相关的垃圾回收规则被触发，Byteman agent 多次尝试加载失败\n2. **frontend 调用超时**：frontend 服务在调用 adservice 时出现 `DeadlineExceeded` 错误\n\n### 根因分析：\n- **主要嫌疑人**：adservice 服务\n- **异常原因**：Byteman agent 的 GC 注入规则导致服务异常，agent 启动失败影响服务可用性\n- **影响范围**：frontend 服务无法正常获取广告信息，出现 RPC 调用超时\n\n这处于初始扫描阶段，需要进一步分析 Trace 数据来确认调用链的异常模式。", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 checkoutservice 到 cartservice 的调用延迟从 2258.79ms 增加到 15998.0ms，延迟倍数约为 7.08。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 cartservice 到 redis 的调用延迟从 1361.25ms 增加到 18490.5ms，延迟倍数约为 13.58。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 frontend 到 adservice 的调用延迟从 5549.49ms 增加到 50902.27ms，延迟倍数约为 9.18。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 checkoutservice 到 emailservice 的调用延迟从 20201.41ms 增加到 87097.5ms，延迟倍数约为 4.31。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 checkoutservice 到 productcatalogservice 的调用延迟从 10547.94ms 增加到 17775.25ms，延迟倍数约为 1.68。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 frontend 到 shippingservice 的调用延迟从 203.09ms 增加到 833.31ms，延迟倍数约为 4.10。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 frontend 到 recommendationservice 的调用延迟从 4045.21ms 增加到 4041.17ms，延迟倍数约为 1.0（无明显变化）。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对异常时间段（2025-06-09T00:10:25Z 至 2025-06-09T00:34:25Z）的监控数据扫描分析，我发现了以下显著的异常情况：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"io_util\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 和 rrt 指标显著异常，p99变化率分别达到1.5674和1.293，表明该服务实例存在严重的响应延迟问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"emailservice-2的rrt_max从正常中位数3075.5ms上升到3821.5ms，p99从7101.98ms飙升到58565.42ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max p99变化率达到1.4408，显示该Pod存在响应时间异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0的rrt_max p99从5071.8ms上升到31209.59ms，同时pod_cpu_usage p99变化率为1.7207\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes中位数下降18.32%，表明该节点内存资源紧张\",\n      \"evidence\": \"aiops-k8s-08节点的可用内存从10.82GB下降到9.01GB，可能影响其上运行的redis-cart-0等服务\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标异常变化，中位数变化率1.1864，同时error_ratio和client_error_ratio出现异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"adservice-0的rrt_max中位数从42534ms下降到10861ms，但error_ratio p99从1.81下降到0.0，可能存在服务状态不稳定\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**主要发现总结：**\n\n1. **服务性能问题**：多个服务的响应时间指标（rrt_max和rrt）出现显著异常，特别是emailservice-2和shippingservice-0实例。\n\n2. **节点资源压力**：aiops-k8s-08节点内存可用量下降明显，可能影响该节点上运行的多个服务。\n\n3. **CPU使用异常**：shippingservice-0的pod_cpu_usage p99变化率达到1.7207，表明CPU使用出现峰值。\n\n4. **服务稳定性问题**：adservice-0出现响应时间大幅波动和错误率变化，可能存在服务不稳定。\n\n这些异常需要进一步深入分析以确定根本原因，特别是关注各服务之间的依赖关系和资源竞争情况。"}
